imagefiles = ImageFileCollection(image_files)
assert len(imagefiles.timestamps_elapsed) == len(image_files)
assert imagefiles.timestamps_elapsed == [image_file.timestamp_elapsed for
    image_file in image_files]
assert imagefiles.timestamps_elapsed_hours == [image_file.
    timestamp_elapsed_hours for image_file in image_files]
assert imagefiles.timestamps_elapsed_minutes == [image_file.
    timestamp_elapsed_minutes for image_file in image_files]
assert imagefiles.timestamps_elapsed_seconds == [image_file.
    timestamp_elapsed_seconds for image_file in image_files]
